    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2. Validation results demonstrate NIH predictions within ±8.7% of FDA benchmark data with RH < 1 at all operating points. The structured requirement record (bindsRequirement) documents flow-rate tolerance bounds (2.5–6.0 L/min ±5%) and pressure-head acceptance criteria (ΔP within ±10% of predicate) as the binding obligations for this package. The package is accepted at Medium assurance level for Class II CPB device submission support.",
